data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!  Looking for privacy? Look no further.  Must see to appreciate this well kept home sitting on almost an acre lot. Walk onto your front porch with swing and enter into a spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home that is completely furnished and ready to move in. Living room has gas fireplace for the winter nights to come. Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances,  lots of cabinet space and counter space along with dinning area. Large master bedroom with separate bath that has stand up shower, claw tub and double vanities. Go down the hall and you will find 2 more bedrooms and a full bath. Off the master bedroom, you will find a screened in porch that overlooks your back yard where you can enjoy your morning coffee. Shed in back has electric.  Large 1 car attached garage and paved driveway. This is one you do not want to miss out on.
